## 1. Install the dependencies

{% if lang.key == 'python' %}
```bash
pip install -r requirements-otel.txt
```
{% elif lang.key == 'node' %}
Merge `package.otel.json` into your `package.json`, then:

```bash
npm install
```
{% elif lang.key == 'java' %}
Merge the entries from `pom-otel.xml` into your `pom.xml`, then:

```bash
mvn -q package
```
{% else %}
Add the modules listed in `go.mod.snippet`:

```bash
go mod tidy
```
{% endif %}

